              <div>
                Many to-go cups have a waterproof inner lining that is made of plastic, which makes them non-recyclable.
                In the US, so many coffee cups are used that 44,110 cups are disposed of every 24 seconds.
                So next time you get a drink, bring your own reusable thermos, cup or mug!
                If you bring your own to Starbucks, you will even get a 50 cent discount.
              </div>
