    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header" id="headingFive">
        <h5 class="mb-0">
          <button class="accordion-toggle btn btn-link collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
            REFUSE THE DRINK LID
          </button>
        </h5>
      </div>
      <div id="collapseFive" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-parent="#challenge-accordion">
        <div class="card-body container">
          <div class="row">
            <div src="" class="col-md-2">
              <%= image_tag("styrofoam.jpg", size: '100x100') %>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-10">
              <div>
                Polystyrene and expanded polystyrene foam — better known as Styrofoam — is one of the most harmful
                forms of waste on the planet. It is rarely recyclable, and, like all plastic, it takes hundreds
                of years to decompose. It is literally everywhere; in our coffee cups, take-out containers, straws,
                cutlery, and more. For this challenge we’re asking you to join the #foamfree campaign that is working
                to ban polystyrene across the nation!
              </div>

